{
  "stem": "22889.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was very strict with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Many, many times used to get a licking from him, and from my father too, once in awhile-- you know, if you didn't do a good job.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After cheder, I came home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my father started to question us, all kind of questions, when he came home from work-- you know, what did you learn?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was very-- my father was very, very strict.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- I don't like it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll be honest with you, I used to hate to go to cheder.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I'm very grateful, today, for that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At least I can sit down with some people that know a little bit about Bible, or [NON-ENGLISH], I can discuss this thing-- which I'm very grateful I learned that.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my sister was always with my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was just a little girl, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember, my mother on Friday used to make the challah, twist challah, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She did about six or seven twists.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my sister, she give a piece of dough, and she used to teach her how to do that, too.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was just a little girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister just started to go to school, yes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were very close family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Don't forget, in our town there was my mother's sister-- two sister, they live in our town, also, and their family.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So Saturday, after lunch they all came to our house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then what do you do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You entertain yourself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My aunt, once-- one of my mother's sister, my aunt, she play mandolin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Her husband play fiddle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they play, and we all sang.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Myself, my kids-- like myself, my brother, we were a little bit older, then-- we went to the Zionist organization.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we learn Hebrew-- not Hebrew, Ivrit.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
